se\\\" on the day, after three arson attacks on the rail system, and France's blaming this on sabotage.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.973393550360407, \"rank\": 0.02557390604717856, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zakharova\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"transport collapse\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"three arson attacks\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"the rail system\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"sabotage\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said the center of Paris was \\\"transformed into a ghetto for homeless people\\\", while \\\"rats flooded the streets\\\".\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999970209501, \"rank\": 2.9790462248959274e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the center\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"a ghetto\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"homeless people\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"rats\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other targets were the U.S. rapper Snoop Dogg carrying the Olympic torch and gaffes such as introducing the South Korean team as North Korea and raising the Olympic flag upside-down.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://