.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an \\\"undesirable\\\" organization\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"our work\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"our staff\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"prosecution\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This follows our earlier unjust labeling as a \\\"foreign agent.\\\"\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our earlier unjust labeling\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"foreign agent\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These actions are direct attempts to silence independent journalism in Russia.\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2576, \"end\": 2582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999774910134333, \"rank\": 1.9273693641797686e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These actions\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"direct attempts\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"independent journalism\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The authorities claim our work \\\"discredits the decisions of the Russian leadership.\\\"\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2648, \"end\": 2655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.7188961396193208, \"rank\": 0.390359104460649, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_